Business Brief -- Tultex Corp.:
   Sportswear Maker Completes
   Acquisition of Logo 7 Inc.
Logo 7 is a leading producer and marketer of professional
sports licensed apparel. It is a licensee of the National
Football League, Major League Baseball, the National Hockey
League, the National Basketball Association and other sports
organizations.
   Tultex, based in Martinsville, Va., said Logo 7 expects to
report 1991 sales of more than $85 million.